title: Watt Dreams May Come
description:
Mina and Ben Solak of The Draft Network discuss potential landing spots for J.J. Watt, provide a holistic view of Carson Wentz' career and forecast his future ceiling, and offer their early assessments of the top 5 quarterbacks in the 2021 Draft Class.
